Installation can be a little complicated, as a licensed copy of [https://www.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transport Tycoon Transport Tycoon Deluxe] is necessary to play OpenTTD.  Soon OpenTTD will be completely open-source and installation will be simple.

'''Click on your operating system in the menu for installation instructions:'''

== Installation on Windows ==
#Get Transport Tycoon Deluxe for Windows. If you don't have your CD, see [http://www.tt-forums.net/viewtopic.php?t=3407 tt-forums.net], or [http://www.google.com/search?q=transport+tycoon+deluxe Google] it.
#Install the game on your computer.
#Download the Windows installer for OpenTTD from the [http://www.openttd.org/downloads.php downloads page].
#Install OpenTTD.
#Tell OpenTTD where to find your TTD files; it should find them automatically if you used the TTD Windows installer.
#Remove the TTD installation if you like.
#Run OpenTTD.


: You can also easily compile the latest [[en/Archive/Community/Nightly build|nightlies]] yourself with [[en/Archive/Community/BuildOTTD]].

== Installation on Mac OS X ==
#Get Transport Tycoon Deluxe for Windows or DOS. If you don't have your CD, see [http://www.tt-forums.net/viewtopic.php?t=3407 tt-forums.net], or [http://www.google.com/search?q=transport+tycoon+deluxe Google] it.
#Create an '''openttd/''' folder on your computer.
#OpenTTD needs the '''data/''' and '''gm/''' directories from TTD, there are a few ways to do this:
#* Copy the folder and files from the TTD game CD to your openttd/ folder.
#* Unzip a TTD installation zip file, and copy the folders.
#* Install TTD for Windows on another partition and then copy the folders.
#Get the OSX installer for OpenTTD from the [http://www.openttd.org/downloads.php downloads page].
#Run OpenTTD.


